Sequence Information.Family: Belongs to the frog skin active peptide family (Brevinin subfamily)
Sequence Information.Target Organism: No MICs found in DRAMP database
Sequence Information.Hemolytic Activity: No hemolysis information or data found in the reference(s) presented in this entry
Sequence Information.Function: This peptide differs from Brevinin-1LTa by only one residue (I vs. V). This conservative change allows to predict that this peptide has all the activities of Brevinin-1LTa.

Literature.Title: The novel antimicrobial peptides from skin of Chinese broad-folded frog, Hylarana latouchii (AnuraRanidae).
Literature.Author: Wang H, Lu Y, Zhang X, Hu Y, Yu H, Liu J, Sun J.
